<p>Digital frames, similar to traditional picture frames, are equipped with high-resolution screens and can be connected to the internet to display your NFT collection. They can be hung on walls or placed on shelves, seamlessly blending with your home decor.</p>



<p>On the other hand, digital screens offer a larger canvas to showcase your art. These screens can be mounted on walls or integrated into furniture, creating a visually striking focal point in any room.</p>



